data.description: Desirable location!!! This house is located on a quiet tree lined street in a prime interior tract in the gorgeous South of Conant neighborhood of Long Beach!  You will love hosting gatherings with friends and family, or enjoying quiet and relaxing summer afternoons with the built-in backyard barbecue and swimming pool. Inside, there's 1344 sq. ft. of living space with central air conditioning and heating, a cozy fireplace, and upgraded windows.  The primary suite is very spacious with an adjacent bathroom and can also act as a second family room or game room.  The home also boasts an impeccable front lawn! This home is very close to Wardlow Park, walking distance to Hartwell Park and Hartwell Golf Course, and is in close proximity to freeways, shopping and restaurants.  This home is everything you could ask for in an East Long Beach home.  Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity!
